subject: CFP
body:
Dear Colleague:

Sorry for cross posting. Please consider contributing to one of the following conferences. 
*************
www.sdiwc.net
*************

The World Congress on E-Commerce and Business on the Web (WCEBW2012) - Technical Co-sponsored by IEEE
Place: United Kingdom
Dates: Aug. 27-29, 2012

The International Conference on E-Learning and E-Technologies in Education (ICEEE2012) - Technical Co-sponsored by IEEE
Place: Poland
Dates: Sept. 24-26, 2012

The International Conference on Computing, Networking and Digital Technologies (ICCNDT 2012)
Place: Bahrain
Dates: Nov. 11-13, 2012

The Third International Conference on Digital Information Processing and Communications (ICDIPC2012)- Technical Co-sponsored by SDIWC
Place: Dubai
Dates: Jan. 30- Feb. 1, 2013

The Second International Conference on Digital Enterprise and Information Systems (DEIS 2013)
Place:  Malaysia
Dates:  March 4-6, 2013

The Second International Conference on e-Technologies and Networks for Development (ICeNd 2013)
Place:  Malaysia
Dates:  March 4-6, 2013

*************
www.sdiwc.net
*************
